dashboard_elements.note_text:
The latest Quarter will always have a lag in meeting Revenue Goal and this is because of the way the data is generated. 

The latest campaigns (the ones in the last quarter) won't see revenue immediately, because there are typically multiple touches before a purchase event occurs. For example, a user may come into the site through a source (Adwords) from a campaign 5 days ago, but that user may come back to the site 10 more times over the course of the next two months before finally making the purchase. That purchase won't be attributed to that campaign and that date until the sale is made 5 months from now.
